defaultprison law 
defaultfirms 
defaultwill be able to absorb 17.5% cuts in fees and the
default reduc
defaulttion in the scope of 
defaultprison law eligible for legal aid, especially given the ongoing proposal that much initial preparation work for judicial review remain unpaid or subject only to discretionary payment.
default22.  Removal of legal aid for prison work mea
defaultn that there will be many important issues where injustice may go unredressed.  For example:
default- miscategorisation of a prisoners
default in too high a security category
default;
