default24.  Work by Dr Nick Armstrong demonstrates that the on-costs 
defaultof the proposed removal of prison legal aid - mainly as  result of prisoners being categorised in too high a security category and an increased number of complaints to the Prisons &amp; Probation Ombudsman.  
